      <h3>6) Redemption Rule (Burn & Settlement)</h3>
      <p>When redemptions are processed:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>tokens are burned (or otherwise permanently removed from circulation via contract mechanism)</li>
        <li>USD is paid out via approved rails under the Redemption Policy</li>
